sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User
    participant API as VELO API
    participant DB as Database
    participant M as Master

    Note over U,M: Commission Flow: "Only from live money"

    rect rgb(255, 245, 235)
        Note over U,DB: Scenario 1: Paid Practice ($50)

        U->>API: Purchase practice ($50)
        API->>DB: user_ledger: -50
        API->>DB: master_ledger: +50 (frozen)
        Note over DB: Master frozen = $50

        Note over M: Practice happens

        M->>API: Mark practice completed
        API->>DB: master_ledger: UPDATE frozen‚Üíavailable
        API->>DB: master_ledger: -7.50 (commission)
        API->>DB: company_ledger: +7.50

        Note over DB: Master available = $42.50<br/>Company earned = $7.50<br/>Commission = 15% of $50
    end

    rect rgb(232, 245, 233)
        Note over U,DB: Scenario 2: Free Practice ($0)

        U->>API: Purchase free practice
        API->>DB: user_ledger: 0
        API->>DB: master_ledger: 0 (frozen)
        Note over DB: Master frozen = $0

        Note over M: Practice happens

        M->>API: Mark practice completed
        API->>DB: master_ledger: UPDATE frozen‚Üíavailable
        Note over DB: NO commission entry!

        Note over DB: Master available = $0<br/>Company earned = $0<br/>Commission = 15% of $0 = $0
    end

    rect rgb(227, 242, 253)
        Note over U,DB: Scenario 3: Company Promo 100% ($50 ‚Üí $0)

        U->>API: Purchase with WELCOME promo
        API->>DB: user_ledger: 0 (user paid $0)
        API->>DB: master_ledger: +50 (frozen)
        API->>DB: company_ledger: -50 (marketing budget)
        Note over DB: Master frozen = $50<br/>Company paid from marketing

        Note over M: Practice happens

        M->>API: Mark practice completed
        API->>DB: master_ledger: UPDATE frozen‚Üíavailable
        Note over DB: NO commission!

        Note over DB: Master available = $50<br/>Company spent = $50<br/>Commission = 15% of $0 (user paid) = $0
    end

    rect rgb(248, 231, 255)
        Note over U,DB: Scenario 4: Master Promo 50% ($50 ‚Üí $25)

        U->>API: Purchase with master promo ALEX50
        API->>DB: user_ledger: -25 (user paid $25)
        API->>DB: master_ledger: +25 (frozen)
        Note over DB: Master frozen = $25<br/>Master gave 50% discount

        Note over M: Practice happens

        M->>API: Mark practice completed
        API->>DB: master_ledger: UPDATE frozen‚Üíavailable
        API->>DB: master_ledger: -3.75 (commission)
        API->>DB: company_ledger: +3.75

        Note over DB: Master available = $21.25<br/>Company earned = $3.75<br/>Commission = 15% of $25 (what user actually paid)
    end

    Note over U,M: Key Principle: Commission = 15% √ó (what user actually paid)

    %% Formulas
    rect rgb(255, 249, 196)
        Note over API,DB: Formulas
        Note over DB: commission_amount = paid_cents √ó 0.15<br/><br/>paid_cents = amount_cents - discount_cents<br/><br/>If paid_cents = 0 ‚Üí NO commission entry
    end
